{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d404d8493c","title":"毛泽东关于中国是否会出修正主义的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7693f0f387","index":0,"year":1966,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"d404d8493c"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ac54e67985","type":"title","text":"关于中国是否会出修正主义","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d404d8493c"},{"id":"bab0b10a96","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d404d8493c"},{"id":"36ef9f6988","type":"paragraph","text":"中国会不会出修正主义当权派的问题，一是出，一是不出；一是早出，一是晚出。还是早出好；搞好了可能不出，在中国出修正主义是困难的。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d404d8493c"},{"id":"f36b1a7803","type":"paragraph","text":"书记处也是分化的，彭、陆、杨、谭、罗等都当过书记处书记，是不断分化，合乎辩证法。有人怕得要死。不分化是主观愿望。中央有，各省也会有。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d404d8493c"}],"page":{"id":"51a21233da","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d404d8493c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}